premise_source_doc_sentence: `` Purple Haze '' is a song written by Jimi Hendrix and released as the second record single by the Jimi Hendrix Experience on March 17 , 1967 .
The expansion pack Vietcong : Fist Alpha was released in 2004 and was bundled with Vietcong as Vietcong : Purple Haze for the PC .
Vietcong : Purple Haze was also released in 2004 for the PlayStation 2 and Xbox , ported by Coyote Games .
